{"tid":893760,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"【突發】忍豆準備出手遊","createTime":"2018-11-08T01:14:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-10T06:17:17.000Z","uid":89435,"like":92,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"0b741ed07134d67d5c19f1264c58f9afed4f6cf2","tid":893760,"uid":89435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T01:14:17.000Z","msg":"【活動】忍豆手遊版測試員招募中<br />\n2018-11-06<br />\n<br />\n嗨各位忍豆們：<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n今天想和你們分享一個消息&mdash;&mdash;許多玩家期待已久的忍豆手遊，已經從構想的蛋孵出小雞囉。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n我們正在製作的忍豆手遊版目前已經完成一個測試版本，為了讓這款遊戲更完整、更接近忍豆玩家的想像，希望能邀請忍豆風雲3的老玩家來實際感受忍豆在手遊上的樣貌，給我們體驗過後的回饋，讓這款遊戲能夠變得更好玩，因此有你的參與是非常重要的！<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n我們預計在11月底～12月初之間，在台北捷運站旁的共同空間舉辦測試；不過由於這次的測試規模很小，因此能夠參與的測試員也不多，所以我們會在下週二（11/13）截止表單，並從中抽選適合的玩家參與測試。如果你是老資歷的忍豆玩家的話（如果剛好又住雙北就更好了），就點開以下的表單填寫吧：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba5226a3d9c8ba0f24998dafcf38df10ed6e5bd4","tid":893760,"uid":191815,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T01:24:00.000Z","msg":"小學雞成日玩"},{"pid":"01b8517a837f7a9a80140ab674acea8d1b2dd315","tid":893760,"uid":115189,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T01:28:14.000Z","msg":"希望唔好係移植版"},{"pid":"ccbff29638defdadfca9aad0f08c86a7785f0445","tid":893760,"uid":89435,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T01:37:06.000Z","msg":"邊個負評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c1dc7b463bc964b9ebec6332b0c6ac891711ef1","tid":893760,"uid":89435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T01:59:28.000Z","msg":"輕輕一pish"},{"pid":"689d548